      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition \u2014 a dependable, well-maintained option for buyers seeking reliable everyday transportation at a fair price. The exterior presents well, showing only the normal minor wear and light surface scratches you'd expect from regular use, with no significant dents or damage to report. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery and trim in good shape, though there are small signs of everyday use consistent with the vehicle's age. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has been properly maintained \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts cleanly, and all major systems are functioning as expected. Brakes, suspension, and steering all feel solid. This is an honest, no-surprises vehicle that will serve a new owner well for daily commuting or family use. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
