    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 and that designation is stated plainly and honestly so buyers know exactly what they're getting into. The exterior shows significant wear: the paint is heavily faded, oxidized, and scratched in multiple areas, with visible dents and rust spots on the body panels. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and a dashboard that shows years of sun damage. Mechanically, the car has known issues \u2014 it runs, but not reliably, and will require meaningful repairs before it can be considered dependable daily transportation. There may be additional underlying issues that a thorough inspection by a qualified mechanic would reveal, and we strongly encourage any interested buyer to do exactly that before purchasing. This vehicle is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project car, or a buyer seeking parts. It is priced accordingly and honestly reflects its current state. No surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
