      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you an accurate picture of what you're getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 paint retains a reasonable shine and color depth, though you'll notice some minor scratches and light surface wear consistent with normal everyday use. There are no major dents, rust issues, or significant body damage to report. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing modest wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but nothing that detracts significantly from comfort or appearance. Mechanically, the vehicle runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, shifts are clean, and all major systems including brakes, suspension, and climate control are in good working order. Tires have reasonable tread remaining. This is a solid, dependable used car that has been maintained responsibly and is ready for daily driving without immediate repair concerns. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged.",
